Capital Markets

Company Overview of Capital International Sàrl



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capital International Sàrl is a privately owned investment manager. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets. It manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds. The firm was founded on July 5, 1963 and is based in Geneva, Switzerland. Capital International Sàrl operates as a subsidiary of Capital Group International Inc.


3 Place des BerguesGeneva,  CH–1201SwitzerlandFounded in 1963



www.thecapitalgroup.com







